[VAR:windows]

[REGION:note]
Already have iTunes installed? [You can skip this section.](Platforms/iOS/QuickStart/2)
[/REGION]

You must have **iTunes** installed in order to package and deploy your iOS projects to your device on Windows.

You can install iTunes from Apple using the following link: [Install iTunes](http://www.apple.com/itunes/)

[![](itunes.png)](http://www.apple.com/itunes/)

Run **iTunes** after it finishes installing.

[/VAR]

[VAR:macos]

[REGION:note]
Already have Xcode installed? [You can skip this section.](Platforms/iOS/QuickStart/2)
[/REGION]

You must have **Xcode** installed in order to package and deploy your iOS projects to your device on Mac OS.

You can install XCode from Apple using the following link: [Install XCode](https://developer.apple.com/xcode/)

[![](DownloadXCode.png)](https://developer.apple.com/xcode/)

Run **Xcode** after it finishes installing.

[/VAR]


